<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_131_r1l1"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Kemnater vogt ʒu <expan>Lawging<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_131_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch geſagt ſey daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l3">leẅt <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Vnd daʒ Jr vnd eẅr <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> vns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenen wolt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l4">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch mıt fleıſſ des guten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l6"><expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . den Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_131_r1l5">vnd eẅr bruder </ab></add> ʒu vns habt . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l7">niht leẅt <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vvurden <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> wır hernach der leẅt <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l8"><expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſo wölten wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darauf bedacht ſein . Denn wo wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l9">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt . etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l10"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Kemnater, vogt zu
                            <expan>Lawging<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt sey, daz wir
                        lewt <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und daz ir und ewr
                                <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> uns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        dienen wolt etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewch mit fleiss des guten <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, den ir <add>und
                            ewr bruder</add> zu uns habt, und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht lewt
                            <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wurden <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        wir hernach der lewt <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> oder
                                <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so wölten wir
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darauf bedacht sein. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
